require(dplyr)
circ2 <- circ1 %>% 
         group_by(grupo) %>% 
         summarise(medini = mean(ini, na.rm =TRUE),
                   med1 = mean(med1, na.rm =TRUE),
                   med2 = mean(med2, na.rm =TRUE))
hist(circ2$medini, freq = FALSE, las = 1)
lines(density(circ2$medini, na.rm = TRUE), col = "red", lwd = 2)

hist(circ2$med1, freq = FALSE, las = 1)
lines(density(circ2$med1, na.rm = TRUE), col = "red", lwd = 2)

hist(circ2$med2, freq = FALSE, las = 1)
lines(density(circ2$med2, na.rm = TRUE), col = "red", lwd = 2)

require(tidyr)
## Loading required package: tidyr
circ3 <- circ2 %>%
         gather(tipo,di√°metro, -grupo)
require(ggplot2)
## Loading required package: ggplot2
medias <- circ3 %>% 
          group_by(tipo) %>%
          summarise(media = mean(di√°metro, na.rm=TRUE))

g1 <- ggplot(circ3, aes(di√°metro, colour = tipo, fill = tipo)) 
g1 + geom_density(alpha= 0.3) +
     geom_vline(xintercept =  14.42478, col = "brown", size = 1) +
     geom_vline(data = medias, aes(xintercept = media, col = tipo), size = 0.5)

Comportamiento de los grupos

require(ggplot2)
require(tidyr)
circ4 <- circ1 %>%
         gather(tipo,di√°metro, -grupo)
circ4$tipo <- factor(circ4$tipo, levels = c("ini", "med1", "med2"))
circ4$grupo <- factor(circ4$grupo)
g2 <- ggplot(circ4, aes(tipo, di√°metro, col = grupo, group = grupo))
g2 + geom_jitter(width = 0.2) + 
  stat_summary(fun.y = "mean", geom = "line") +
  guides(col = guide_legend(ncol = 2)) +
  geom_hline(yintercept =  14.42478, col = "brown", size = 0.7)
